name: Behind FROGCRYPTO
description: Hop along on a journey for a behind the scenes look of FrogCrypto. We'll decode the secrets of these unique digital frogs, each minted with cryptographic authenticity. Discover the diverse biomes, frog temperaments, and how zero-knowledge proofs make these digital amphibians not just collectibles but testbeds for programmable cryptography.

speakers.name: Forest Fang
speakers.bio: Forest is a software engineer on the Crypto team at Stripe. He is a 0xparc community developer and recently has been working with the PCD team on Zupass.
